      "NESO FES 2024 fuel price assumptions"
    ],
    "base_year": 2024,
    "gas_price_assumption": "55 p/therm (2024 central estimate)",
    "carbon_price_assumption": "45 GBP/tCO2 (UK ETS 2024)",
    "notes": "SRMC = fuel_cost/efficiency + carbon_cost × emissions_factor + VOM. Start-up and ramp costs are linear approximations added to SRMC for snapshot dispatch."
